<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>361</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shì dào hēi àn zhǔ lā zhe wǒ men de shǒu
 jiù xiàng dà hǎi dài zǒu nà měi yī tiáo hé liú
 jiào huì hé yī pàn wàng le hǎo jiǔ
 dì xiōng hé mù tóng jū yǒu shén guì zhòng de yóu,
 zǒu a áng qǐ tóu
 dōu rè qíng de shēn chū wēn nuǎn de shuāng shǒu,
 shēng mìng hé de quán shuǐ qīng chè jiàn dǐ,
 yǒng xiàng zhǔ de guó dù yǒng jiǔ dào yǒng jiǔ.</lyrics>
<title>jiào huì hé yī 迦南361</title>
</song>